<title type="html"><![CDATA[I'm very new at this, but I'm having a strange problem:]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=303&amp;p=1982#p1982"><![CDATA[
The NES can only display 8 sprites per scanline.  If you need to have more sprites per scanline, you'll have to rotate the order of the sprites in OAM.  This will cause flickering, but at least all the sprites will be visible.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=120">Tom</a> — Mon May 02, 2005 5:09 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
